txt.en: 'You are a stranger indeed if you know little of Gondor. The kingdom is very old, older than I could say, and has not been ruled by a king for many hundreds of years. Steward Denethor rules in Minas Tirith, but to my knowledge he has never come to Morlad.\n\n'A king would be no different, I expect. No king would worry himself with our troubles in the Blackroot Vale.'
What can you tell me about Gondor?
